"12\" alt>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"title-block w-100\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                        FOR BODY. FOR RELAX.</p>\n                                    <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showName\">\n                                        WELLNESS</h3>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div><div class=\"embla__slide slider-image item active\" mbr-style=\"{'margin-left': gap + 'rem', 'margin-right': gap + 'rem'}\">\n                        <div class=\"slide-content\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"item-img\">\n                                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/468816837-17885098407171534-3883517077450125905-n-removebg-preview.png-1-447x559.png\" data-slide-to=\"13\" data-bs-slide-to=\"13\" alt>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"title-block w-100\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                        FOR BODY. FOR RELAX.</p>\n                                    <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showName\">\n                                        WELLNESS</h3>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div><div class=\"embla__slide slider-image item active\" mbr-style=\"{'margin-left': gap + 'rem', 'margin-right': gap + 'rem'}\">\n                        <div class=\"slide-content\">\n                            <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                <div class=\"item-img\">\n                                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/468924202-17885098782171534-7882424421744783464-n-removebg-preview.png-1-447x559.png\" data-slide-to=\"14\" data-bs-slide-to=\"14\" alt>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"title-block w-100\">\n                                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                        FOR BODY. FOR RELAX.</p>\n                                    <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showName\">\n                                        WELLNESS</h3>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <button class=\"embla__button embla__button--prev\">\n                <span class=\"mobi-mbri mbri-left mbr-iconfont\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                <span class=\"sr-only visually-hidden visually-hidden\">Previous</span>\n            </button>\n            <button class=\"embla__button embla__button--next\">\n                <span class=\"mobi-mbri mbri-right mbr-iconfont\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n                <span class=\"sr-only visually-hidden visually-hidden\">Next</span>\n            </button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
